Feature-tile screenshots go here.

Name each file after the feature slug, e.g. auto-fix.png, and reference
it from that feature's front matter (docs/features/auto-fix.md) as:

    image: img/features/auto-fix.png

The homepage tile frames it as a dark terminal window, so dark-mode
terminal captures (~16:10, e.g. 960x600) look native. Adding the
`image:` field also needs an optional `image?` leaf on the `feature`
kind schema in .mdsmith.yml.
